      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "When everything feels like it's broken, the desire for the noise to simply stop can feel like the only escape. Please understand that feeling this exhaustion is a sign of deep pain, not a reflection of your inherent worth. While I cannot replace professional help, please know that giving yourself a chance to talk to someone trained in these moments can sometimes provide a temporary, vital shift in perspective. Reaching out again, even if it feels repetitive, can connect you with immediate human support.",
